      "Implementation strategy: ① IAM hardening — Enforce MFA on top of SSO (SAML 2.0/OIDC). Admin accounts require hardware security keys (FIDO2); learners use OTP or biometrics. Role-based session timeouts (admin: 15min, learner: 60min) prevent idle session hijacking.",
