      "High Availability (HA) architecture essentials: ① Load balancer (ALB/NLB) — Distributes traffic across multiple web/app servers, eliminating single points of failure (SPOF). 10-second health checks immediately remove unhealthy servers from routing ② Auto-scaling — Automatically provisions servers when CPU exceeds 70% and scales down during low traffic. Pre-scheduled 3x capacity expansion for compliance training deadline weeks.",
