      "DR strategy tiers based on RPO and RTO: ① Cold Standby (RTO 24h) — Lowest cost, non-critical systems. Manual backup restoration ② Warm Standby (RTO 1-4h) — Reduced-scale standby environment always running ③ Hot Standby (RTO 15min) — Full-scale standby with real-time sync ④ Active-Active (RTO 0) — Both regions serve traffic simultaneously for true zero-downtime.",
