      "cmi5 is a profile built on top of xAPI that adds interoperability rules between LMS and content. While xAPI offers flexibility to 'record anything freely,' cmi5 defines standardized rules for course registration, session start/end, and completion determination, ensuring compatibility between LMS and content. As of 2025, cmi5 is called the 'next-generation SCORM.'",
